cz.cvut.fel.matyapav.afandroid.builders.skins

Class DefaultSkin

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cvut.fel.matyapav.afandroid.builders.skins.DefaultSkin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Skin

    public class DefaultSkin
extends java.lang.Object
implements Skin
    This class represents default implementation of Skin interface and will be used if user did not specify own skin. User's skins should extends this class because it gives ability to define only needed parts of skin.
    Since:
    1.0.0.
